                "Have you ever compared this to past experiences and felt relieved?",
                "Do I make you want to be a more patient version of yourself?",
                "What‚Äôs something about love you understand better now that we talk?",
                "What do you admire about how I handle emotions?",
                "What part of me do you find rare‚Äînot just romantic, but real?",
                "If I asked you what kind of lover you hope to become, what would you say?",
                "What‚Äôs one thing you‚Äôd do differently in love now because of me?"
